{"id":160,"ayahs":[{"number":74,"arabic":"وَٱذْكُرُوٓا۟ إِذْ جَعَلَكُمْ خُلَفَآءَ مِنۢ بَعْدِ عَادٍۢ وَبَوَّأَكُمْ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ تَتَّخِذُونَ مِن سُهُولِهَا قُصُورًۭا وَتَنْحِتُونَ ٱلْجِبَالَ بُيُوتًۭا ۖ فَٱذْكُرُوٓا۟ ءَالَآءَ ٱللَّهِ وَلَا تَعْثَوْا۟ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ مُفْسِدِينَ","translation":"\"And remember how He made you heirs to [the tribe of] `Ad and settled you firmly on earth, so that you [are able to] build for yourselves castles on its plains and hew out mountains [to serve you] as dwellings: remember, then, God's blessings, and do not act wickedly on earth by spreading corruption.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1028.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":61586,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱذْكُرُوٓا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা স্মরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61587,"position":2,"arabic":"إِذْ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61588,"position":3,"arabic":"جَعَلَكُمْ","translation":"বানিয়েছিলেন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61589,"position":4,"arabic":"خُلَفَآءَ","translation":"স্থলাভিষিক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61590,"position":5,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61591,"position":6,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61592,"position":7,"arabic":"عَادٍۢ","translation":"আ'দের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61593,"position":8,"arabic":"وَبَوَّأَكُمْ","translation":"ও প্রতিষ্ঠিত করেছিলেন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61594,"position":9,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61595,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61596,"position":11,"arabic":"تَتَّخِذُونَ","translation":"তোমরা নির্মাণ করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61597,"position":12,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61598,"position":13,"arabic":"سُهُولِهَا","translation":"সমতল ভূমির তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61599,"position":14,"arabic":"قُصُورًۭا","translation":"প্রাসাদসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61600,"position":15,"arabic":"وَتَنْحِتُونَ","translation":"তোমরা খোদাই করে তৈরী করেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61601,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْجِبَالَ","translation":"পাহাড়গুলোতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61602,"position":17,"arabic":"بُيُوتًۭا ۖ","translation":"বসতঘরসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61604,"position":18,"arabic":"فَٱذْكُرُوٓا۟","translation":"অতএব তোমরা স্মরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61605,"position":19,"arabic":"ءَالَآءَ","translation":"অনুগ্রহগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61606,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61607,"position":21,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61608,"position":22,"arabic":"تَعْثَوْا۟","translation":"অনাচার সৃষ্টি করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61609,"position":23,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61610,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61611,"position":25,"arabic":"مُفْسِدِينَ","translation":"বিপর্যয় সৃষ্টিকারী হয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_074_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61612,"position":26,"arabic":"٧٤","translation":"(৭৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":75,"arabic":"قَالَ ٱلْمَلَأُ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟ مِن قَوْمِهِۦ لِلَّذِينَ ٱسْتُضْعِفُوا۟ لِمَنْ ءَامَنَ مِنْهُمْ أَتَعْلَمُونَ أَنَّ صَٰلِحًۭا مُّرْسَلٌۭ مِّن رَّبِّهِۦ ۚ قَالُوٓا۟ إِنَّا بِمَآ أُرْسِلَ بِهِۦ مُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"The great ones among his people, who gloried in their arrogance towards all who were deemed weak, said unto the believers among them: \"Do you [really] know that salih has been sent by his Sustainer?\" They answered: \"Verily, we believe in the message which he bears.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1029.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":62167,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62168,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَأُ","translation":"(সেই জাতির) প্রধান ব্যক্তিরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62169,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62170,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟","translation":"অহংকার করেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62171,"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62172,"position":6,"arabic":"قَوْمِهِۦ","translation":"জাতির তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62173,"position":7,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"উদ্দেশ্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62174,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱسْتُضْعِفُوا۟","translation":"যাদেরকে দুর্বল করে রাখা হয়েছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62175,"position":9,"arabic":"لِمَنْ","translation":"(তাদের)কে যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62176,"position":10,"arabic":"ءَامَنَ","translation":"ঈমান এনেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62177,"position":11,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ","translation":"মধ্য হতে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62178,"position":12,"arabic":"أَتَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"\"কি তোমরা জানো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62179,"position":13,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62180,"position":14,"arabic":"صَـٰلِحًۭا","translation":"সালেহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62181,"position":15,"arabic":"مُّرْسَلٌۭ","translation":"(সত্যিই) প্রেরিত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62182,"position":16,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"পক্ষ হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62183,"position":17,"arabic":"رَّبِّهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তার রবের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62185,"position":18,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62186,"position":19,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"\"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62187,"position":20,"arabic":"بِمَآ","translation":"দিয়ে ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62188,"position":21,"arabic":"أُرْسِلَ","translation":"তাকে পাঠানো হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62189,"position":22,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62190,"position":23,"arabic":"مُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"বিশ্বাসী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_075_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62191,"position":24,"arabic":"٧٥","translation":"(৭৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":76,"arabic":"قَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱسْتَكْبَرُوٓا۟ إِنَّا بِٱلَّذِىٓ ءَامَنتُم بِهِۦ كَٰفِرُونَ","translation":"[But] the arrogant ones said: \"Behold, what you have come to believe in we refuse to regard as true!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1030.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":62499,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62500,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62501,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱسْتَكْبَرُوٓا۟","translation":"অহংকার করেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62502,"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"\"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62503,"position":5,"arabic":"بِٱلَّذِىٓ","translation":"উপর যার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62504,"position":6,"arabic":"ءَامَنتُم","translation":"তোমরা ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62505,"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"প্রতি তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62506,"position":8,"arabic":"كَـٰفِرُونَ","translation":"প্রত্যাখ্যানকারী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_076_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62507,"position":9,"arabic":"٧٦","translation":"(৭৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":77,"arabic":"فَعَقَرُوا۟ ٱلنَّاقَةَ وَعَتَوْا۟ عَنْ أَمْرِ رَبِّهِمْ وَقَالُوا۟ يَٰصَٰلِحُ ٱئْتِنَا بِمَا تَعِدُنَآ إِن كُنتَ مِنَ ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ","translation":"And then they cruelly slaughtered the she-camel and turned with disdain from their Sustainer's commandment, and said: \"O Salih! Bring about that [punishment] with which thou hast threatened us, if thou art truly one of God's message bearers!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1031.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":62774,"position":1,"arabic":"فَعَقَرُوا۟","translation":"অতঃপর তারা হত্যা করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62775,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاقَةَ","translation":"মাদি উটটিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62776,"position":3,"arabic":"وَعَتَوْا۟","translation":"ও তারা অমান্য করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62777,"position":4,"arabic":"عَنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62778,"position":5,"arabic":"أَمْرِ","translation":"নির্দেশ (পালন করা)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62779,"position":6,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","translation":"রবের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62780,"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَالُوا۟","translation":"এবং তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62781,"position":8,"arabic":"يَـٰصَـٰلِحُ","translation":"\"হে সালেহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62782,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱئْتِنَا","translation":"কাছে এসো আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62783,"position":10,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"নিয়ে ঐ বিষয় যার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62784,"position":11,"arabic":"تَعِدُنَآ","translation":"তুমি ধমক দিচ্ছো আমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62785,"position":12,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62786,"position":13,"arabic":"كُنتَ","translation":"হও তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62787,"position":14,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62788,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ","translation":"রাসূলদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_077_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62789,"position":16,"arabic":"٧٧","translation":"(৭৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":78,"arabic":"فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ ٱلرَّجْفَةُ فَأَصْبَحُوا۟ فِى دَارِهِمْ جَٰثِمِينَ","translation":"Thereupon an earthquake overtook them: and then they lay lifeless, in their very homes, on the ground.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1032.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":63475,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ","translation":"অতঃপর গ্রাস করলো তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_078_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63476,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلرَّجْفَةُ","translation":"ভূমিকম্প","audioUrl":"wbw/007_078_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63477,"position":3,"arabic":"فَأَصْبَحُوا۟","translation":"অতঃপর তারা হয়ে গেলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_078_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63478,"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_078_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63479,"position":5,"arabic":"دَارِهِمْ","translation":"ঘরের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_078_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63480,"position":6,"arabic":"جَـٰثِمِينَ","translation":"উপুড় হয়ে পড়ে থাকা অবস্থায় অর্থাৎ মৃত পড়ে রইলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_078_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63481,"position":7,"arabic":"٧٨","translation":"(৭৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":79,"arabic":"فَتَوَلَّىٰ عَنْهُمْ وَقَالَ يَٰقَوْمِ لَقَدْ أَبْلَغْتُكُمْ رِسَالَةَ رَبِّى وَنَصَحْتُ لَكُمْ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تُحِبُّونَ ٱلنَّٰصِحِينَ","translation":"And [Salih] turned away from them, and said: \"O my people! Indeed, I delivered unto you my Sustainer's message and gave you good advice: but you did not love those who gave [you] good advice.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1033.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":63880,"position":1,"arabic":"فَتَوَلَّىٰ","translation":"অতঃপর সে মুখ ফিরালো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_079_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63881,"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ","translation":"থেকে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_079_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63882,"position":3,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_079_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63883,"position":4,"arabic":"يَـٰقَ